title: Grateful Dead Live at Merriweather Post Pavilion on 1985-06-30
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> CC Rider-> Brown Eyed Women, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Keep On Growing-> Big Railroad Blues-> Looks Like Rain-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Shakedown Street-> Samson & Delilah, Gimme Some Lovin'-> He's Gone-> Cryptical Envelopment-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Around & Around-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: D5 A Sony D5 was used to record this show, as well as all other shows from Summer 1985 through the Fall of1989. After which, either a Panasonic SUV 250 or 255 was used up until the summer of 1995.
